list.name: Default
list.comment: Add a dropdown to select a grouping. Define a second grouping in the settings file. Change which grouping is used when the dropdown changes. Note: group values are not re-calculated. The dropdown does not control which grouping is being used, only causes a change.

task.summary: Use AngularJS, drop Backbone/React. Use WebStorm to edit and manage source files.
Added page top. Added side menu. Added a google chart for bill trends, sample data is hard-coded.

Asynchronous data retrieval in the controller, using Promise and Then.
